---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Hyperliquid — Perp DEX + Pre-IPO">
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-24">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Perp DEX + Pre-IPO Stock Perps</span><span class="lang-zh">永續合約DEX + Pre-IPO股票合約</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-8">Hyperliquid</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-zinc max-w-none text-zinc-400 text-[15px] leading-relaxed space-y-6">

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Hyperliquid is a crypto perpetual futures exchange doing $5 to $10 billion in daily volume — on par with Bybit and OKX — but running entirely on its own Layer 1 blockchain. Up to 50x leverage, no KYC, no trading hours, 24/7/365. Its onchain orderbook engine, HyperCore, processes roughly 200,000 orders per second. The user experience feels like a centralized exchange, but all order matching and settlement happens onchain.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Hyperliquid係一間crypto永續合約交易所，日交易量$50至$100億 — 同Bybit、OKX同級 — 但完全運行喺自己嘅Layer 1區塊鏈上。最高50倍槓桿，無KYC，無交易時間限制，24/7/365。其鏈上訂單簿引擎HyperCore每秒處理約200,000個訂單。用戶體驗感覺似centralized exchange，但所有order matching同settlement都喺鏈上進行。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">But the product that should capture the attention of Hong Kong finance professionals is not the crypto perps — it's the pre-IPO stock perpetual futures.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">但真正應該引起香港金融從業者注意嘅產品唔係crypto perps — 係pre-IPO股票永續合約。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Pre-IPO Stock Perps: HIP-3</span><span class="lang-zh">Pre-IPO股票永續合約：HIP-3</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">You help them close deals, write valuations, meet management — but you can't buy a single share. Now there's a market where you can express your view.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">你幫佢哋做deal、寫valuation、見management — 但買唔到一股。而家有個market俾你express你嘅view。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Hyperliquid's HIP-3 protocol, launched in October 2025, enables permissionless deployment of perpetual futures markets. Platforms built on top of it offer perp exposure to pre-IPO company valuations: SpaceX, OpenAI, Anthropic, Cursor, Stripe, and more. These are not equity instruments — they are pure valuation speculation contracts that settle against the latest funding round price or IPO price.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Hyperliquid嘅HIP-3協議於2025年10月推出，允許無需許可地部署永續合約市場。基於其構建嘅平台提供對pre-IPO公司估值嘅永續合約敞口：SpaceX、OpenAI、Anthropic、Cursor、Stripe等。呢啲唔係股權工具 — 係純估值投機合約，以最新融資輪價格或IPO價格結算。</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The numbers are significant. Pre-IPO perps represent over 35% of all Hyperliquid trading volume — not a niche product. Open interest across pre-IPO markets hit $1.43 billion. Leverage is up to 10x, lower than crypto perps because the underlying liquidity is thinner. Trading volume on traditional asset perps surged 162% from $11.8 billion in December 2025 to $31.0 billion in January 2026, reaching $40.6 billion in cumulative volume by early February.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">數字係顯著嘅。Pre-IPO永續合約佔Hyperliquid總交易量超過35% — 唔係小眾產品。Pre-IPO市場未平倉量達到$14.3億。槓桿最高10x，比crypto perps低因為底層流動性較薄。傳統資產永續合約交易量從2025年12月嘅$118億激增162%至2026年1月嘅$310億，到2月初累計交易量達$406億。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">The Infrastructure</span><span class="lang-zh">基礎設施</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Hyperliquid runs its own L1 chain with a proprietary consensus mechanism called HyperBFT. It is not built on Ethereum or Solana. The chain is purpose-built for trading: all order matching and settlement happens onchain, with sub-second finality. To deposit, you bridge USDC from Arbitrum to the Hyperliquid L1.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">Hyperliquid運行自己嘅L1鏈，使用自研嘅HyperBFT共識機制。唔係建立喺Ethereum或Solana之上。呢條鏈係為交易而專門設計：所有order matching同settlement都喺鏈上進行，具有亞秒級finality。要充值，你需要從Arbitrum將USDC跨鏈到Hyperliquid L1。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Risks and Transparency</span><span class="lang-zh">風險同透明度</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The decentralization claims deserve scrutiny. The validator set is only 21, with the team controlling the majority. The bridge is controlled by 4 team addresses — not a multisig in any meaningful sense. In March 2025, a trader manipulated the JELLY token price; the team responded by overriding the oracle price and force-liquidating positions. Arthur Hayes commented: "stop pretending Hyperliquid is decentralized."</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">去中心化嘅聲稱值得審視。驗證者集合只有21個，團隊控制大多數。Bridge由4個團隊地址控制 — 在任何有意義嘅層面都唔係multisig。2025年3月，一個trader操縱JELLY代幣價格；團隊嘅回應係override oracle定價並強制清算倉位。Arthur Hayes評論：「唔好再扮Hyperliquid係去中心化。」</span>
      </p>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">The risk factors are real: smart contract exploits on the bridge or matching engine, oracle manipulation (proven possible by the JELLY incident), unilateral team intervention in market rules, and no regulatory oversight — Hyperliquid is not an SFC-licensed VATP. Hong Kong traffic accounts for approximately 6% of the platform's user base. There is no KYC, which means no deposit protection and no recourse.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">風險因素係真實嘅：bridge或matching engine嘅智能合約漏洞、預言機操縱（JELLY事件已證明可能）、團隊單方面干預市場規則，以及無監管監督 — Hyperliquid唔係SFC持牌VATP。香港流量約佔平台用戶群嘅6%。無KYC，即無存款保障且無追索權。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Context</span><span class="lang-zh">香港背景</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">For Hong Kong finance professionals, the platform's primary value is in the pre-IPO stock perps. The sector knowledge and valuation insights you accumulate through your work — deal flow, management meetings, industry analysis — can be directly applied here. You're trading against a participant base that largely lacks your information advantage. But understand clearly: this is not a regulated product, there is no investor protection, and the team has demonstrated willingness to intervene in markets unilaterally. Size your positions accordingly.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">對香港金融從業者而言，平台嘅主要價值在於pre-IPO股票永續合約。你通過工作累積嘅行業知識和估值洞察 — deal flow、管理層會面、行業分析 — 可以直接應用於此。你在與大部分缺乏你信息優勢嘅參與者交易。但要清楚理解：呢個唔係受監管產品，冇投資者保障，而且團隊已展示過單方面干預市場嘅意願。相應調整你嘅倉位規模。</span>
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-16 mb-6">
        <span class="lang-en">Getting Started</span><span class="lang-zh">如何開始</span>
      </h2>

      <p>
        <span class="lang-en">Connect any EVM wallet (MetaMask, Rabby), bridge USDC from Arbitrum to the Hyperliquid L1, choose between crypto perps and pre-IPO stock perps, and set your leverage. Start with low leverage — 2 to 3x maximum is recommended for anyone new to the platform.</span>
        <span class="lang-zh">連接任何EVM錢包（MetaMask、Rabby），從Arbitrum跨鏈USDC到Hyperliquid L1，選擇crypto永續合約或pre-IPO股票永續合約，設定槓桿。建議低槓桿開始 — 對平台新手而言，最高2至3x。</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-cyan-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Explore other onchain products</span><span class="lang-zh">了解其他鏈上產品</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">Polymarket for prediction markets. AMM for permissionless liquidity.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">Polymarket做prediction markets，AMM做permissionless liquidity。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href={`${base}/products/polymarket`} class="px-5 py-2.5 bg-cyan-500 text-black text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-cyan-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Polymarket</a>
        <a href={`${base}/products/amm`} class="px-5 py-2.5 border border-zinc-700 text-white text-sm rounded-lg hover:border-zinc-500 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">Onchain AMM</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
